modName: SKSE - ENBinjector ONE CLICK BATCH File
summary: Open up your ENB injector and SKSE in one click.
descriptionHtml:
SKSE - ENBinjector ONE CLICK BATCH File
*********************************************************
A simple batch file to run ENB injector and SKSE in one click.

Instructions:
*****************
>Download the file, right click and edit with notepad.
>Replace the line[b] \Skyrim\ENBInjector.exe [/b] with the one on your computer.
>Replace the line [b]\Skyrim\Skse_injector.exe[/b] with the one on your computer.
>Save.

P.S.
*****
Place the file anywhere you want, think of it as a shortcut that opens multiple things at once.
author: LennyKrapitz
